\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2020\/04\/06\/allah-loves-concessions\/","url_meta":{"origin":21086,"position":0},"title":"Hadith on Rukhsa: Allah loves believers taking His concessions","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 6, 2020","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Abbas reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cVerily, Allah loves for you to take His concessions, just as He loves you to fulfill His edicts.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Ibn H\u0323ibba\u0304n 354 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Arna\u2019ut \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0650 \u0627\u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0639\u064e\u0628\u0651\u064e\u0627\u0633\u064d \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u0650\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":32091,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/06\/15\/allah-loves-kindness-easy\/","url_meta":{"origin":21086,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Rifq: Allah loves kindness, making things easy","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 15, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdullah ibn Mughaffal reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cVerily, Allah is gentle and he loves gentleness. He gives for it what is not given for harshness.\u201d Source: Sunan Abi\u0304 Da\u0304wu\u0304d Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Albani Al-Azimabadi said, \u201cAllah loves gentleness, meaning, kindness\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":13102,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/03\/24\/women-gold-silk-halal\/","url_meta":{"origin":21086,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Clothing: Women can wear gold and silk, not men","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"March 24, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Musa reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cVerily, Allah Almighty has made lawful silk and gold for the women of my nation, but he has forbidden them for men.\u201d Source: Sunan al-Nasa\u0304'i\u0304 5265 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a \u0645\u064f\u0648\u0633\u064e\u0649 \u0623\u064e\u0646\u064e\u0651\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":11819,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/01\/25\/allah-loves-see-blessings\/","url_meta":{"origin":21086,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Bounties: Allah loves to see His blessings on His servants","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"January 25, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Zuhayr ibn Abi 'Alqamah reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cVerily, Allah Almighty loves to see the traces of blessings on his servant. He does not love one who wallows in misery and pessimism.\" Source: al-Mu\u2019jam al-Kabi\u0304r 5167 Grade:\u00a0Sahih\u00a0(authentic) according to Al-Suyuti \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0632\u064f\u0647\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0631\u0650\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0